  <title>Correlation</title>

  <introduction>
    <p>
      This chapter introduces correlation as a measure of the linear
      relationship between two numeric variables. You will learn how to compute
      and interpret correlation coefficients, visualize relationships with
      scatter plots, and understand the distinction between correlation and
      causation.
